data.description: This charming 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom home in Northeast Cape's family-friendly neighborhood is the ideal first-time buyer's haven. With a fenced yard, easy-to-maintain tile flooring, a modern kitchen, and recent plumbing upgrades in 2019, it offers both comfort and peace of mind. The full reverse osmosis system ensures clean water, and its location provides access to parks and amenities. Don't miss out on this cozy gem in Northeast Cape – your perfect first home awaits! SELLER HIGHLY MOTIVATED, BRING OFFERS!!!!
